<p><strong>1</strong></p>
<p><strong>录取通知书发放时间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200820/71a9ac675a16496cacf60908aceb9c08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
